Text: Why is it compressed into 20 *.rar files?
It's a damn fake! Avoid people.

They have renamed the rars before and it's been alright. Just a joke I suppose. But I'll write here if there's anything weird with the file. No idea why they split up the files, but sceneline is usually one of the most trustworthy luckily.
